text: Ihenacho is both a given name and surname. Notable people with the name include: *Carl Ihenacho (born 1988), American football player *Duke Ihenacho (born 1989), American football player *Kennedy Ihenacho (born 1990), Nigerian musician *Leo Ihenacho (born 1977), British singer ==See also== *Ego Ihenacho Ogbaro, Nigerian musician
